snippet.title: IHLSBMCILSIREIKTFTDL Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The current game trailer for 'I Have Low Stats But My Class Is "Leader", So I Recruited Everyone I Know To Fight The Dark Lord'! You primarily play as the main character Josephine, fated to defeat the Dark Lord. However, as she's generally unskilled in combat, she recruits literally everyone in her hometown to fight enemies with a party of 99 characters!

You can find the current build at:


Itchio (w/demo):https://cannibalinteractive.itch.io/i-have-low-stats-but-my-class-is-leader-so-i-recruited-everyone-i-know

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1176040/I_Have_Low_Stats_But_My_Class_Is_Leader_So_I_Recruited_Everyone_I_Know_To_Fight_The_Dark_Lord/
